How to compile and run the c++ files, anything with .cpp

chmod u+x (name of file) only once
g++ (name of file).cpp -o (name output file) `pkg-config --cflags --libs opencv`
./(name output file

How to compile and run c files, anything with .c
chmod u+x (name of file) only once
gcc (name of file).c -o (name output file) `pkg-config --cflags --libs opencv`
./(name output file

How to compile and run python files, anything with .py
chmod u+x (name of file) only once
python (name of file).py
Not 100% sure bout this

How to compile with wiringPi
 gcc master.c -o master -lwiringPi

How to compile main2.cpp
g++ main2.cpp -o main `pkg-config --cflags --libs opencv`
./main camera setup
